		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Try converting it to 4-color indexed (i.e. paletted) in some graphics tool (Photoshop, IrfanView, whatever) before copy-pasting it.<br /><br />P.S. You can import a 256x240 BMP file to NES Screen Tool directly.

		

